@[name]

@[title]
string.insert()
@[title]

@[text]
@[code]
string.insert( str : string, index = 0, remove = 0, copy = 0 )
@[code]
Insert substring @[cyan]str@[cyan] at @[cyan]index@[cyan].
If @[cyan]remove@[cyan] is greater than zero, @[cyan]remove@[cyan] characters
